description:
Take a look at Philippi from the sky; located in Greece - northwest of the nearby island of Thasos, in this Cinematic Aerial Film. When filming for the Lineage 'Pentecost to Patmos' series, we captured some incredible views from the skies of Greece.

 Main Episode: https://youtu.be/g_mK8LiKFoA
 Behind the Scenes #1: https://youtu.be/ntJAZyLnZMY
 Behind the Scenes #2: https://youtu.be/fmfzHhfRn3w


The city of Philippi was the first one that Paul would minister in in Europe after receiving the Macedonian call. It was here where Lydia was converted and baptised and Paul and Silas were locked up in prison before the jail keeper was converted. The start of Pauls missionary work here wasnt easy.
